### 12. Agent registry tests (`aitbc/agent_registry/tests/`)

**Fix:** Added `type: ignore[import-not-found]` on the first `import app` / `from app import ...` in each test file. Subsequent imports in the same file don't need the ignore (mypy resolves `app` from the first import). These imports work at test runtime (when CWD is the agent_registry directory) but mypy cannot resolve them during static analysis from the project root.

